{"tid":1949342,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【入嚟統戰】不分黃藍沒得結婚擺酒，但是鄉黑鄧家就有特權？","createTime":"2020-03-29T14:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T15:35:11.000Z","uid":167548,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"73826334bdc3eef7a68e5aa69ac9a84042d3eb3b","tid":1949342,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:30:35.000Z","msg":"即使你是藍到發黑, 紅到發紫, 你都冇特權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n你地是Nothing ar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;支持政府都冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;鄉黑鄧家就是太上皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#1極速神驅&nbsp;<br />\n粉嶺龍躍頭鄧家娶新抱 祠堂外宴請逾百人 每枱多於4人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949249</a><br />\n<blockquote>【21:35】警方表示，晩上7時許，有人投訴上水萃雲路祠堂村內有一批人辦婚宴，已派員前往了解。<br />\n<br />\n政府公佈禁止4人以上公眾群聚活動，仍有人堅持辦婚宴酒席。粉嶺龍躍頭今日晚上有鄉紳為慶祝娶新抱，在祠堂設宴款待親友。據知，一對新人男方是民建聯前北區區議員鄧根年的侄兒。<br />\n<br />\n記者下午現場所見，松嶺鄧公祠外一處空地設有一個類似婚宴主持平台，另設置約20圍枱，每圍枱設置8至10張膠櫈，至近傍晚6時，賓客陸續入場，每枱已放好盤菜加熱，至一對新人上場說話及有歌舞表演助慶後，晚上7時半開席，各圍枱陸續坐滿賓客，惟每張枱最多只有6至8人，部分更呈現「吉枱」狀態，其間有村民不滿記者拍攝，更走出場外驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n鄧根年接受《蘋果》電話查詢時承認，今晚是其胞弟的兒子娶妻，「傳統婚事，時間改唔到，圍村整咗﹝嘢食﹞，叫咗人，改都改唔切 」，強調已要求賓客入場前消毒，枱與枱亦會隔開1.5米，「佢哋有事，我哋都麻煩！」<br />\n<br />\n鄧指今次婚禮大約有百多人獲邀，「開咗十零廿圍，百零人左右，但有分開幾個一圍，一圍就五六個人」。他稱由於疫情嚴竣，未及晚上8時許，賓客已走近一半，希望大眾體諒傳統圍村人辦喜宴的難處，不停強調「差唔多完啦，大家體諒」，及後匆匆掛線。<br />\n<br />\n松嶺鄧公祠於16世紀初為紀念開基祖鄧松嶺公而建，屬龍躍頭鄧氏的祠堂，現為法定古蹟。<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"4ee8909eb2dd7c3a527bef2d454544dc0311ea49","tid":1949342,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de6760bdefa35b9f9f34435644bf68f8a86feeab","tid":1949342,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:31:55.000Z","msg":"捧殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捧殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />捧殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3360bea3fefb81508b991b64f4ed21c75808172","tid":1949342,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:05.000Z","msg":"guo"},{"pid":"462fae4a2fa2cc9c661679b8e48c735f70a1dfbb","tid":1949342,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"fuck you asshole"},{"pid":"d51f20dee44df8780e145dd3019e914e312d15d1","tid":1949342,"uid":322044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定有人咳到甩肺"},{"pid":"35b1c69a7ea1b8b0b54e39875f213c9e3679afc7","tid":1949342,"uid":17838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"47c62c69d8b64bb5138bdb03bc24c22e27cefd3d","tid":1949342,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"燉炳強是唔是想坐上曱種個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ac5ff2e24b4bdee8d681652e44c1fa603cbac4","tid":1949342,"uid":132999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:33:41.000Z","msg":"中哂咪好囉"},{"pid":"ea3aa1fa865e1802aeb5cc39dea24602dcf20ef0","tid":1949342,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"462fae4a2fa2cc9c661679b8e48c735f70a1dfbb","tid":1949342,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"fuck you asshole"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T14:33:41.000Z"